" zZ to toggle folds recursivily
nnoremap zZ zA
vnoremap zZ zA

" za to open all folds
nnoremap za zR
vnoremap za zR

" zA to close all folds
nnoremap zA zM
vnoremap zA zM

" Make zO recursively open whatever top level fold we're in, no matter where the
" cursor happens to be.
nnoremap zO zCzO

